# Assets Credit Card Amount

## identifier
de7476

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of credit card balances receivable by the reporting party as at the relevant date. This item is to be determined in accordance with accounting standards.

A credit card is a card whose holder has been granted a revolving credit line up to a pre-arranged limit.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.CreditCard.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
